snippet.title: Ghost In The Barn House Official Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
#steam #indiegame #horror
Check out Ghost In The Barn House on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1219220/Ghost_In_The_Barn_House/
Ghost In The Barn House is a 2D Survival Horror game based on the story of an old Haunted barn which was built in the 1800s in Texas.
